# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Privacy boundary: personal memory & generated outputs are PRIVATE.
# Never commit or push them to a public remote.
# The shareable artifact is the card/ (logic + default templates) only.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Private data — state (who you are), goal (where you're going), action (what you do).
# Never commit. Keep only the folder-skeleton READMEs so the STRUCTURE stays shareable.
state/**
!state/**/
!state/**/README.md
goal/**
!goal/**/
!goal/**/README.md
action/**
!action/**/
!action/**/README.md

# Darwinian Minds — generated / materialized state (regenerate with `drwn write`).
# The portable pin is tracked in .agents/drwn/config.json. The lock contains
# machine-specific store paths, so each user should generate it locally.
/.claude/
/.codex/
/.cursor/
/.mcp.json
/.agents/skills/
/.agents/drwn/*
!/.agents/drwn/config.json

# LaTeX build artifacts
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.fls
*.fdb_latexmk
*.synctex.gz

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
